*

1. On *piješ* čaj svaki dan. (He drinks tea every day.) 
2. Ona *pije* kafu sa mlekom. (She drinks coffee with milk.) 
3. Oni *piju* vodu iz reke. (They drink water from the river.) 
4. Ona *piješ* sok uveče. (She drinks juice in the evening.) 
5. Mi *pijemo* vino na večeri. (We drink wine in the evening.) 
6. Oni *piju* pivo za zabavu. (They drink beer for fun.)